        <h3 class="title"><a href="http://brickybox.com/2013/03/29/netatmo-menu-bar-app-for-osx" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link: Netatmo Menu Bar app for OSX">Netatmo Menu Bar app for OSX</a></h3>

        <!-- story header -->
        <div class="postheader">
