        <div class="postbody entry clearfix">
         <p><img src="http://bone.buckleycomputers.ie/tayto-20130330-161925.png" alt="Netatmo Menu Bar Screenshot" align="right" />For some peculiar reason, Netatmo don&#8217;t have an OSX app for viewing their devices (however their iOS one is simply brilliant). So, me being me, I wrote one. Very simple app to put together in fact (but then, it doesn&#8217;t do all the fancy history stuff that the iOS one does).<br />
